festival.introText:
Anomaly presents Summer of Love Trance Festival 2023 in conjunction with Thirty & Psychonauts

Dare To Be Different.... 

The biggest names in trance & dance music all together on a beautiful farm in the gorgeous Clent Hills just outside Birmingham

3 Stages Across 2 Days // 35+ Mega Acts // Open Air Main Stage

Massive After Party

Trance, House, Techno, Hardcore + More
Friday 12th August 2022 - 14:00-23:00
Saturday 13th August 2022 - 12:00-23:00

Licensed bar & food stalls on site
This is an 18+ event.

 
Afterparty:
Renegade System | Daniel Skyver | Glojin | Sholan | Tasso | Will Renville | B-3 | Dom Harper | Donny Mac | Doug Drelincourt | Stereotype | Isaac Vivian
 
Hosts: Anomaly | Thirty | Psychonauts

 

IMPORTANT INFO

This is a green field site, please be aware of ground conditions.
Prolonged exposure to amplified sound may cause permanent hearing damage.
Strobe lighting and smoke effects may be used at the Event.
The Event is outdoors so you are strongly advised to bring appropriate footwear and clothing, including warm clothing for the night period.
There will be outlets on site selling food and drink.
Please respect the residents in the surrounding area and enter and leave as quietly as possible.
Please keep the field, site and nearby streets tidy, use litter bins provided.
Alcohol will not be permitted into the festival area from outside.
Drivers enter car parks at own risk, uneven surfaces likely, this is a green field site.
We do not accept any liability for break-ins, damage and/or theft.

General Enquiries
info@anomalyuk.com

Press Enquiries
rich@anomalyuk.com

Sponsorship Enquiries
if you are interested in becoming a brand partner of ASOL, please contact Rick:
finance@anomalyuk.com

LOCATION

Anomaly Fields, B620JN

faqs.question: Is there onsite camping at Anomaly Summer of Love Festival?
faqs.answer: Yes there is camping available, a ticket is necessary for entry.

faqs.question: disabled access information
faqs.answer: Disabled facilities are available. Please contact us in advance of the Event at info@anomalyuk.com if you have any specific access requirements, otherwise it may not be possible to meet your needs.

faqs.question: How much are Anomaly Summer of Love Festival tickets?
Are payment plans available for Anomaly summer of love festival?
faqs.answer: yes, payment plans are available for the festival starting from £20+bf for the deposit.

faqs.question: Where is Anomaly Summer of Love Festival?
faqs.answer: Anomaly Summer of Love Festival takes place in Halesowen, Bromsgrove Road, B62 0JN

faqs.question: How much are camping ticket for Anomaly summer of love festival?
faqs.answer:
camping day tickets are available from £10 +bf

camping weekend tickets are available from £15 +bf

faqs.question: Am I allowed to bring food and drink into Anomaly Summer of Love Festival?
faqs.answer: Food & Drink will not be allowed in the festival area from outside.

faqs.question: How much is a car park ticket?
faqs.answer:
car park day tickets are from £5 +bf

car park weekend tickets are from £10 +bf

faqs.question: Can I re-enter Anomaly Summer of Love Festival?
faqs.answer: Once you enter the main site you must stay in the main site. Once you leave you will NOT be allowed to re-enter the site.

faqs.question: What is the dress code for Anomaly Summer of Love Festival?
faqs.answer:
Flower Power, Peace & Love, it is the summer of love after all.

Dress for the weather, dress for a festival and dress with attitude!

news.title: Anomaly Summer of Love will return in Aug 2022 - Phase 1 DJ's Announced
news.summary: Following the success of the 2020 Covid restricted edition, Anomaly Events have decided to go all out and re-launch the biggest outdoor trance only festival in the UK with 28 global based DJ's performing plus an Afterparty.
